g src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3ccef28cf31c46d27f2260dcbddb84389677ef","tid":1889731,"uid":197690,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"b09a471ccfd14f69e844b4c21850ce1909877870","tid":1889731,"uid":197690,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:36:25.000Z","msg":"上次啲狗得罪方丈報<br />\n嚇個前線記者<br />\n自此之後除咗因航仲有因警<br />\n不過留意返<br />\n方丈報骨子仍然係藍<br />\n歸類為 撐共 但不太撐狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKJN1Pe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKJN1Pe.jpg&h=fa9dfe37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然比起721 831等等黎講唔算係咩大事<br />\n但大家唔好太善忘<br />\n偶爾都要温故一吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435c5a7fb630fc9414eb66e8baf7cac638774d55","tid":1889731,"uid":69544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71bf5048445f92bf371d5e3ac821a33d4ce8b1e1","tid":1889731,"uid":286309,"like":2,"dislike":34,"score":-32,"quote":{"pid":"cd5f3d59582b6924cd71cefe5bbcb5e1d75e5c2b","tid":1889731,"uid":174174,"like":17,"dislike":16,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:31:31.000Z","msg":"東方前線好多黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:34:38.000Z","msg":"好啦，咁大家原諒東方啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:40:56.000Z","msg":"前線係咪黃我唔知，間野就絕對唔係黃"},{"pid":"159ab8445e307d81f53101db5089ffc81b84b439","tid":1889731,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6b8567e0d7b786d2d6c079bdf79bd58794b01ac","tid":1889731,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:40:21.000Z","msg":"俾左信就大晒，好似係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:41:07.000Z","msg":"小編本人駕到？"},{"pid":"caa7a394a07d81b81aeeba087ab9e46e89182579","tid":1889731,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2469d9bfa6ff44b221823136d587f4594867c386","tid":1889731,"uid":199670,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:37:45.000Z","msg":"認真睇哂佢plz <br />\n<br />\nTerry Yeung:<br />\n新聞跑來了。「文宣平台」複製貼上，再推農場內容謀利；兩登網友群起轉發，內容被一覽無遺。<br />\n<br />\n點擊沒了，連帶的商業價值都被抹殺。有些媒體，如《蘋果》，更是走會員制。<br />\n<br />\n試問，你忽然尊重的媒體工作者，要怎樣謀生？<br />\n<br />\n半年來，愈見惡化。議題被網民壞習慣，以及網軍的無形之手操控。<br />\n<br />\n然後你說：運動靜咗好多。<br />\n<br />\n改變自己，改變習慣。<br />\n<br />\n1. 不是正統媒體的新聞，不轉發。<br />\n2. 未經Fact Check、來自內容農場的消息，不要理。<br />\n3. 很多文宣大台都是盜取內容，不轉發。<br />\n4. 只轉發原創者的內容<br />\n5. 貼報道上討論區，只取少量內容，放link鼓勵點擊（尢其文宣大台該帶頭做）。<br />\n<br />\n再重覆，目標為上，才可以拯救連登垂死的熱門。<br />\n<br />\n比方說，<br />\n1. 如果兩日後有遊行，專注推行動Post；<br />\n2. 同一議題，集中處理，不要分散；<br />\n3. 有人留言「拉」，網友不需再留言；<br />\n4. 戒除政治J女性癖，不要再討論區議員身材；<br />\n5. 未能Fact Check的事情，忍痛讓佢沉。<br />\n6. 減少用極端字眼，例如「就嚟輸」；<br />\n7. 至為重要：不 要 再 推 假 標 題<br />\n<br />\n每個手足都有責任打好呢場資訊戰，改變習慣，重奪輿論主導權，大家一定做得到。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube戰線：黃色資訊片一律Coment+Like+Share&amp;Subscribe（CLS)（share做唔到的話重要片先share)<br />\n<br />\n香港人，改變。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.如果覺得有意思，煩請分享，謝謝你。<br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\nIG：Terry_yeung_blog<br />\nIG連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IMS6HI&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=f60fea51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:41:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ff4ca4045fb5e00a96d7cf489b4ea74aa8f8db3","tid":1889731,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:41:18.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"f379ecb5da68429da6f16540a475f631396d7f72","tid":1889731,"uid":279401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpfHQJn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpfHQJn.jpg&h=6c19858a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a3bd5fe3a0428ede9dc59ba46ba